{"tid":113534,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"IVE ENGG 都算係最好既 Sub degree","createTime":"2017-02-09T05:07:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-09T06:26:29.000Z","uid":14170,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e7dec928da56ff5ef530b3f5f250633a866a6b52","tid":113534,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T05:07:17.000Z","msg":"最簡單 ASSO ENGG 畢業唔夠資格拎 B 牌，IVE 夠 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nSpace EEE HD 畢業連 Machines, Power Electronics, Building services 計下 Cable size, relay 幾秒 trip 點做 discrimination 都唔識 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢個 HD 笑死人咩，根本係 asso 課程黎叫咩 HD <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f5ce849160257254231a338c77ef0b654b3a109","tid":113534,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T05:12:05.000Z","msg":"而 IVE 完全捨棄電子，谷哂落 AC/DC circuit analysis, power distribution and transmission line, Power Elec., Machine and Drives, Electrical installation and Building Services 度 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n完全係大學 year3 &amp; 4 既 courses <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然無咁難無咁理論，但 IVE 旨在每個領域都比少少知識你，再加上全年既 Practical Training，你會知道自己計緊咩學緊咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔似大學一味 plug in 數，然後禁機得出答案。問班大學生學緊咩計緊咩，完全唔知 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f943c0f22e12457087da9c8de1f54375d2fcc37","tid":113534,"uid":68364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T05:12:21.000Z","msg":"Eng 入面 EE 最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4686af0a80b534fc174026271f1d0f5b9225aab0","tid":113534,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy